<p class="ayah 3-29" id="29" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Whether</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُخْفُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you conceal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صُدُورِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your breasts</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُبْدُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you disclose it -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمْهُ ٱللَّهُ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah knows it.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَعْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He knows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰ