<p class="ayah 3-30" id="30" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(On the) day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجِدُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will find</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمِلَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَيْرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّحْضَرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">presented,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمِلَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُوٓءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr