<p class="ayah 3-31" id="31" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`If</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُحِبُّونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">love</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱتَّبِعُونِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then follow me,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُحْبِبْكُمُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah will love you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَغْفِرْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He will forgive</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُنُوبَكُمْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your sins.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَفُورٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Oft-Forgiving,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar q