<p class="ayah 3-36" id="36" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَضَعَتْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">she delivered her,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">she said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`My Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَضَعْتُهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] (have) delivered [her]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُنثَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a female.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">knows better</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[of] what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَضَعَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">she delivered,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَيْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and is not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلذَّكَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the male</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَٱلْأُنثَىٰ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like the female.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`And that I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَمَّيْتُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] (have) named her</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَرْيَمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Maryam</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنِّىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُعِيذُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] seek refuge for her</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in You</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَذُرِّيَّتَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and her offspring</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Shaitaan</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّجِيمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rejected.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>36<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 3-37" id="37" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَقَبَّلَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So accepted her,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">her Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِقَبُولٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with acceptance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسَنٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنۢبَتَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and made her grow -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَبَاتًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a growing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسَنًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَفَّلَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and put her in (the) care</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زَكَرِيَّا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Zakariya.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Whenever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَخَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">entered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهَا زَكَرِيَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Zakariya in her</span></span><span 