d ltr" dir="ltr">Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْزُقُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">gives provision</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِغَيْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">without</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حِسَابٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">measure.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>37<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
