<p class="ayah 3-39" id="39" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَنَادَتْهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then called him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Angels</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when he</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَآئِمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) standing -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُصَلِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">praying</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمِحْرَابِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer chamber.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُبَشِّرُكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">gives you glad tidings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِيَحْيَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of Yahya,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُصَدِّقَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">confirming</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span c