<p class="ayah 3-65" id="65" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَهْلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O People</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Book!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Why</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُحَآجُّونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) you argue</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">concerning</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِبْرَٲهِيمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Ibrahim</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُنزِلَتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">was revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلتَّوْرَٮٰةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Taurat</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْإِنجِيلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the Injeel</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنۢ بَعْدِهِۦٓ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after him?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span clas