<p class="ayah 3-68" id="68" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْلَى ٱلنَّاسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the best people (to claim relationship)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِإِبْرَٲهِيمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Ibrahim</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّبَعُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">follow him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّبِىُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] Prophet</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe[d].</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِىُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a Guardian</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the 