<p class="ayah 3-78" id="78" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَفَرِيقًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely (is) a group -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَلْوُۥنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they distort</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلْسِنَتَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their tongues</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْكِتَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in (reciting) the Book</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِتَحْسَبُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that you may think it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Book</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) from</span></span><span class="word staticWo