<p class="ayah 3-94" id="94" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱفْتَرَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">fabricates</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكَذِبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] lie</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنۢ بَعْدِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">after</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then those -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّـٰلِمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) the wrongdoers.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>94<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
