<p class="ayah 3-96" id="96" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوَّلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) first</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">House</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وُضِعَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">set up</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلنَّاسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the mankind</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the one which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِبَكَّةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) at Bakkah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُبَارَكًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">blessed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُدًى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and a guidance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the worlds.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>96<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
