<p class="ayah 3-109" id="109" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And to Allah (belongs)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُرْجَعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will be returned</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأُمُورُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the matters.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>109<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
