<p class="ayah 3-121" id="121" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَدَوْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you left early morning</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your household</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُبَوِّئُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to post</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the believers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَقَـٰعِدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to take) positions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلْقِتَالِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the battle.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَمِيعٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) All-Hearing,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">All-Knowing.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>121<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 3-122" id="122" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَمَّت</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">inclined</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَّآئِفَتَانِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">two parties</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَفْشَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they lost heart,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيُّهُمَا‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) their protector.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيَتَوَكَّلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">let put (their) trust</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the believers.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>122<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 3-123" id="123" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَصَرَكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">helped you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِبَدْرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in Badr</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while you (were)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَذِلَّةٌ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">weak.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱتَّقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَعَلَّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that you may</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَشْكُرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(be) grateful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>123<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
