<p class="ayah 3-151" id="151" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَنُلْقِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We will cast</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلُوبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) hearts</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرُّعْبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] terror</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">because</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَشْرَكُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they associated partners</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُنَزِّلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He sent down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top fi