<p class="ayah 3-180" id="180" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (let) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَحْسَبَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">think</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَبْخَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">withhold</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاتَـٰهُمُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah (has) given them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَضْلِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">His Bounty</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(that) it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَيْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّهُم‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl"